        "1_story": "Imagine you are solving a complex calculation in an exam. BODMAS helps you decide the correct order to solve each part, ensuring you get the right answer every time.",
        "2_definitions": [
            "üí° BODMAS: The rule that defines the order of operations‚ÄîBrackets, Orders (powers/roots), Division, Multiplication, Addition, Subtraction.",
