            "üí° Division: Splitting into equal parts (√∑ or /).",
            "üí° Multiplication: Repeated addition (√ó or *).",
            "üí° Addition: Combining numbers (+).",
            "üí° Subtraction: Taking away from a number (-).",
            "üí° Nested Brackets: Brackets within brackets.",
            "üí° Left to Right Rule: For operations of same rank, solve from left to right.",
            "üí° Expression: A combination of numbers and operations."
        ],
        "3_formula_bank": [
            "üßÆ BODMAS order: Brackets > Orders > Division/Multiplication > Addition/Subtraction",
            "üßÆ (a + b) √ó c = a √ó c + b √ó c",
            "üßÆ a^m √ó a^n = a^(m+n)",
            "üßÆ a^m / a^n = a^(m-n)",
            "üßÆ (a + b)^2 = a^2 + 2ab + b^2",
            "üßÆ (a - b)^2 = a^2 - 2ab + b^2",
            "üßÆ (a + b)(a - b) = a^2 - b^2",
            "üßÆ 1/a + 1/b = (a + b)/ab",
            "üßÆ 1/a - 1/b = (b - a)/ab",
            "üßÆ (a + b + c)^2 = a^2 + b^2 + c^2 + 2(ab + bc + ca)"
        ],
        "4_micro_examples": [
